blocks.text: The following analysis may help you understand your MAIN PROCESS FLOWS.  A first analysis can be performed using the "Process Discovery" widget, shown below, to investigate how many events and execution paths are performed. Additionally, you can switch to the "Cycle Time" metric to see which execution paths take more time during the execution.

The process execution path analysis enables you to better understand how your process is executed. The process paths on top of our reference process model stress the primary process flows. In addition, you find your Best-Run Scores for the different execution steps below. You can use this to prioritize your process improvements.

dataSource.query:
SELECT 
    count(case_id) FILTER (WHERE "event_name" MATCHES ((
		'Create invoice via BAPI interface' |
        'Create invoice via EDI/IDoc' |
        'Create invoice via evaluated receipt settlement' |
        'Create invoice via background invoice verification' |
        'Create invoice via system user' |
        'Create invoice via SRM or Ariba'
	))) / count(case_id) * 100
    
FROM THIS_PROCESS

SELECT 
    count(case_id) FILTER (WHERE "event_name" MATCHES ((
		'Move invoice immediately to free for payment' |
        'Block invoice automatically via invoice verification'
	))) / count(case_id) * 100
    
FROM THIS_PROCESS

SELECT 
    count(case_id) FILTER (WHERE "event_name" MATCHES ((
		'Release payment block via invoice verification' |
        'Move invoice immediately to free for payment'
	))) / count(case_id) * 100
    
FROM THIS_PROCESS

SELECT 
    count(case_id) FILTER (WHERE "event_name" MATCHES ((
		'Clear FI-AP items via payment run'
	))) / count(case_id) * 100
    
FROM THIS_PROCESS

columnConfigurations.columnName: COUNT(case_id) / COUNT(case_id) + COUNT(case_id) / COUNT(case_id) + COUNT(case_id) / COUNT(case_id) + COUNT(case_id) / COUNT(case_id) / 4 * 100

dataSource.query:
SELECT 
	"1 - Main - Company Code (BUKRS)" AS "Company Code",
    COUNT(1) AS "Number of Cases",
	
    (COUNT (CASE_ID) FILTER (WHERE "event_name" MATCHES (('Create invoice via BAPI interface' |'Create invoice via EDI/IDoc' |'Create invoice via evaluated receipt settlement' |'Create invoice via background invoice verification' |'Create invoice via system user' |'Create invoice via SRM or Ariba'
	    ))) / COUNT(CASE_ID)
    + COUNT(CASE_ID) FILTER (WHERE "event_name" MATCHES (('Move invoice immediately to free for payment' |'Block invoice automatically via invoice verification'
	    ))) / COUNT(CASE_ID)
    + COUNT(CASE_ID) FILTER (WHERE "event_name" MATCHES (('Release payment block via invoice verification' |'Move invoice immediately to free for payment'
        ))) / COUNT(CASE_ID)
    + COUNT(CASE_ID) FILTER (WHERE "event_name" MATCHES (('Clear FI-AP items via payment run'
        ))) / COUNT(CASE_ID)
    ) / 4  * 100 AS "Best-Run Score: Overall",

    COUNT (CASE_ID) FILTER (WHERE "event_name" MATCHES ((
		'Create invoice via BAPI interface' |
        'Create invoice via EDI/IDoc' |
        'Create invoice via evaluated receipt settlement' |
        'Create invoice via background invoice verification' |
        'Create invoice via system user' |
        'Create invoice via SRM or Ariba'
	))) / COUNT(CASE_ID) * 100 AS "Best-Run Score: Invoice Creation (%)",
        COUNT(CASE_ID) FILTER (WHERE "event_name" MATCHES ((
		'Move invoice immediately to free for payment' |
        'Block invoice automatically via invoice verification'
	))) / COUNT(CASE_ID) * 100 AS "Best-Run Score: Invoice Blocking (%)",
    COUNT(CASE_ID) FILTER (WHERE "event_name" MATCHES ((
		'Release payment block via invoice verification' |
        'Move invoice immediately to free for payment'
    ))) / COUNT(CASE_ID) * 100 AS "Best-Run Score: Release for Payment (%)",
      COUNT(CASE_ID) FILTER (WHERE "event_name" MATCHES ((
		'Clear FI-AP items via payment run'
    ))) / COUNT(CASE_ID) * 100 AS "Best-Run Score: Payment (%)"

FROM THIS_PROCESS
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY 2 DESC
